      <title>贝莱德曾经强大的通胀对冲 ETF 正在失去王冠</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/blackrock-s-once-mighty-inflation-hedge-etf-is-losing-its-crown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曾经占据主导地位的贝莱德公司 (BlackRock Inc.) 债券 ETF 在向投资者宣传了充满利率风险的安全交易的危险后，有可能失去同类最大通胀对冲产品的桂冠。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/blackrock-s-once-mighty-inflation-hedge-etf-is-losing-its-crown</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通的 Sippel 退出，由 Rokos 接任，Thakur 成为市场主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/jpmorgan-names-thakur-sole-global-markets-head-as-sippel-exits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司全球市场联席主管 Jason Sippel 将离职，转投对冲基金 Rokos Capital Management，而 Pranav Thakur 将接任这家华尔街最大交易部门的唯一主管。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/jpmorgan-names-thakur-sole-global-markets-head-as-sippel-exits</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:40:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>坠机事件再次引发对华盛顿空域拥挤的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-31/crash-revives-concerns-over-crowded-dc-airspace-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国航空公司一架喷气式飞机与一架黑色直升机在空中相撞，再次引发了人们对罗纳德·里根华盛顿国家机场上空拥挤空域的担忧。美国国家运输安全委员会正在领导调查。泰勒·肯德尔在里根的“彭博监视”节目中报道此事。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-31/crash-revives-concerns-over-crowded-dc-airspace-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:40:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>钢铁制造商 Celsa 开始向西班牙投资者出售 20% 股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/steelmaker-celsa-starts-process-to-sell-20-to-spanish-investor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，钢铁制造商 Celsa Group 已启动向西班牙投资者出售高达 20% 股份的程序，这是 2023 年批准的重组计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/steelmaker-celsa-starts-process-to-sell-20-to-spanish-investor</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:33:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非再次停电，结束了连续 10 个月的停电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/south-african-power-cuts-return-ending-eskom-s-10-month-streak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非国家电力公司将在其部分电厂发生故障后恢复断电，结束了长达 10 个月的停电，这既为该公用事业公司赢得了赞誉，也引发了人们对其业绩好转是否可持续的怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/south-african-power-cuts-return-ending-eskom-s-10-month-streak</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 13:08:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
